snippet.title: Adventure Time: Hey Ice King! Why'd You Steal Our Garbage?! (3DS) Trailer
snippet.description: Nintendo Life -- Following its initial debut during the Adventure Time panel at Comic Con 2012, here's a teaser trailer for Nintendo DS / Nintendo 3DS title Adventure Time: Hey Ice King! Why'd You Steal Our Garbage?! Find out more at http://www.nintendolife.com/games/3ds/adventure_time_hey_ice_king_whyd_you_steal_our_garbage
